To create react file
(have to install node.js )
create a folder and open with vscode(optional cause i use vscode for total lesson)
open a terminal console on loacal folder and run

npx create-react-app <name>

This will create a react lib folder for your work

To run live server run

cd to folder

run : npm start


Components:

components refers user interface

components types:

	stateless Function componenet
		javascript Functions
		code 1

	stateful class components
		class extending component class
		Render methon returning HTML
		code2 2






